    "theoretical": { n: 'Theoretical chemistry relies on mathematical formulas derived from quantum mechanics to predict the energies and behavior of molecular states.', q: 'What computational method solves the Schrödinger equation approximately to determine molecular electron structures?', o: ['Density Functional Theory (DFT)', 'Monte Carlo', 'Navier-Stokes', 'Euler Method'], a: 'Density Functional Theory (DFT)' },
